{"tid":1932133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"說好的罷睇？我要上熱門post 《YouTuber 暗地藍到發黑》認清楚佢地unfollow!","createTime":"2020-03-18T14:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T12:26:33.000Z","uid":330821,"like":103,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"230bb596941ebadfd8e53ec9d6d5365ca9ae943f","tid":1932133,"uid":330821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢兩條友一邊譴責手足，一邊賺緊黃絲錢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於岩岩轆緊ig story <br />\n見到我有fd igstory祝福依兩條友結婚🙃<br />\n我實在忍唔住要爆料, 其實我都見到有人係佢個行山片 留言話佢係 《錫安教》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydmLFBW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydmLFBW.png&h=f4dc007c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubj9nKn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fubj9nKn.png&h=ef8ae49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解仲咁多人睇緊佢?? 黎以諾同佢女朋友wing<br />\n雖然佢地無表明過佢既政治立場, 但我必須公開佢既原因係 佢含家都係返錫安教.<br />\n<br />\n佢老豆老母可以話係元老級, 所以黎以諾返錫安係由細返到大！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moSi0B4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoSi0B4.png&h=c3eb98a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錫安教, 眾所週知係俾人認定&lt;邪教&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hNbBa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hNbBa2.png&h=2309b21a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDbzyXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDbzyXJ.png&h=4f039045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGrjK4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGrjK4q.png&h=8a194de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我可以講佢係異端教會，錫安教 &rsquo;教主&lsquo;日撚日分享啲講導信息 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">《全部都係譴責示威者係暴徒》</span>，而且係由雨傘運動個陣已經開始評激示威者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V09EK55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV09EK55.png&h=11dd4c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呢到淨係想講重點, 錫安教講所以關於《譴責示威者》嘅信息 全部你地可以自己上網search！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地唔撚係仲睇啊!? 你地睇佢啲片YouTube會分紅 靠view賺錢, 你睇左姐係袋錢佢地落袋<br />\n你地咁樣對得住一班 手足屋企無得返，又俾屋企封鎖經濟到無錢開飯？ <br />\n</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足們!! 說好的黃色經濟圈?<br />\n麻煩睇左請廣傳, 加推上熱門🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.unfollow - 罷睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClLuwJ0Sde6IgVxkn83nPCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUClLuwJ0Sde6IgVxkn83nPCg&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=0b783df3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClLuwJ0Sde6IgVxkn83nPCg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.unfollow ig 同 罷買佢間ig shop</span><br />\nig: enoch70612<br />\nIg: vanwing<br />\nShop ig: albatross_twoeyesss</span>"},{"pid":"092973ba176ad4af7ee6363d636031bdcca0a7fe","tid":1932133,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"【媒體懶人堂】三招對抗藍絲文宣戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932182</a>"},{"pid":"efb66a4592471f136d87953550d6247e1224ce66","tid":1932133,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a61acb00bcd69112973377abe6c6516434aa8bb7","tid":1932133,"uid":107571,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"Who?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2c073228861a2775b7bd43d2307dc92c3ee1c8","tid":1932133,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"冇人推？"},{"pid":"29a0a866d678b312e0c0e45711ac3e79a88015c2","tid":1932133,"uid":330821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a61acb00bcd69112973377abe6c6516434a